{"tid":1280161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懇求大家 日後有咩抗爭 一定要好好保護自己身份","createTime":"2019-07-03T01:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T07:26:45.000Z","uid":61886,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4a0c8c677acde6759bf6eecdeea129eb41845ea9","tid":1280161,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"無論你係前線 定係後排 甚至運物資都好<br />\n剩係一個口罩係唔足夠<br />\n希望大家 最少最少都要戴到咁 兩樣一齊著<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYhNneR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYhNneR.png&h=b5e5ffe0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tC07neR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtC07neR.png&h=000611f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明白係好熱 透氣都覺得辛苦<br />\n或者後排覺得 我都無做咩衝擊行為 唔使咁大陣仗啦<br />\n<br />\n我想講既係<br />\n其一係<br />\n警犬而家無差別拉人<br />\n無論你有無做啲咩 佢地就算明知charge你唔入<br />\n有機會都會拉人 消磨你意志 或者等你自爆<br />\n雨革果時已經係咁 大家都要小心<br />\n<br />\n其二係 <br />\n如果我地夠多人一齊戴足裝備<br />\n係可以大大保護埋前線既義士<br />\n加大搜證既難度<br />\n令義士無咁易被入罪<br />\n前線既可以著埋依啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CfDdhP2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCfDdhP2.png&h=1f0f53a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請求大家<br />\n一定一定要記住 <br />\n我地唔可以再失去任何戰友<br />\n<br />\n保護自己 保護義士<br />\n齊上齊落"},{"pid":"c92d4986d56bcfacc41f80afd13e39d91e3ad298","tid":1280161,"uid":89429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:26:12.000Z","msg":"口罩係好焗好唔舒服  但真係任何時候都唔好撚除"},{"pid":"5be52aecda23be7283219c0382fa15eaefb01843","tid":1280161,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e039fe3ed1cdd69a30215805db7eb4b41188216","tid":1280161,"uid":107023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c92d4986d56bcfacc41f80afd13e39d91e3ad298","tid":1280161,"uid":89429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:26:12.000Z","msg":"口罩係好焗好唔舒服  但真係任何時候都唔好撚除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:28:20.000Z","msg":"遮樣的口罩可以吉幾個窿透氣"},{"pid":"bbb5fcd702bf908360dd6c56274931f23df0f8f4","tid":1280161,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb54bcb10aef4be795e883a0684b6895db7187f","tid":1280161,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f290d728f8b6b0eb78c263822f05e697f984503f","tid":1280161,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T01:55:20.000Z","msg":"一向都係帽加口罩，朋友見到都認石出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b8fd92751bd8e193e8ec3f805ff22c99da35bf","tid":1280161,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d9acba4f8b71797ddc5a21de285c90f2d268b8","tid":1280161,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:06:05.000Z","msg":"啲狗專係查著黑衫嘅人<br />\n<br />\n不如下次著多幾隻色衫或者帶多件衫換都好"},{"pid":"a5461a40874b0dfccba7623d18ec61efc3175074","tid":1280161,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:27:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6236f2356777bf95eabb3dd63910503ab45f4997","tid":1280161,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:30:11.000Z","msg":"鞋都買對全黑冇花紋嗰啲"},{"pid":"ca9c58ce71bc810fb9ef2fec38d810f948cdd204","tid":1280161,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:37:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cff4ca58a2d6110f66720e1285eb31cd8aa083e","tid":1280161,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T02:42:04